author: Evelyn Cheng
title: 'Not unreasonable' for China's economy to shrink 10% in the first quarter, independent survey shows
description: An early look at Chinese business conditions in March shows little indication the economy has recovered much from the shock of the new coronavirus in the first two months of the year, according to the China Beige Book.
